%% Diagram: Bootstrap initialization flow for SSR (Next.js)
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser
    participant Next as Next.js server
    participant Core as Statsig Server Core SDK
    participant Client as @statsig/js-client

    Browser->>Next: GET /page
    Next->>Core: getClientInitializeResponse(user, {hashAlgorithm:'djb2', filters})
    Note over Core: In-memory evaluation against<br/>cached config spec
    Core-->>Next: Bootstrap JSON (filtered)
    Next-->>Browser: HTML with inlined bootstrap JSON
    Browser->>Client: new StatsigClient(key, user)
    Browser->>Client: client.dataAdapter.setData(json)
    Browser->>Client: client.initializeSync()
    Note over Client: details.reason = 'Bootstrap'<br/>No /initialize round-trip
    Client-->>Browser: Synchronous checkGate / getExperiment
